Puerto Rico's Health Information Directory API.

Developed using Grails 2.2.1


To use:
1- Login using credentials username:me password: password
2- Navigate to  ListProfessionalsController to see results.
3- Field based security is defined in the Manage Fields in Roles


Features:
Spring Security Enabled
Brute Force Detector for Login Attempts
Flexible Design based on field based and role based security
Data is exposed as JSON

Future Enhancements:
Include more methods that filter results
Include method for validating the information of a professional
Include navigation
